&lt;li&gt;Manage contract negotiations and renewals, collaborating with shared services&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor client contracts, service level agreements (SLAs), and key performance indicators (KPIs) to ensure service excellence.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with the Commercials Team to manage account budgets, forecasts, and financial performance, ensuring accuracy and account profitability&lt;/li&gt;
